usage: node ./index.js tenant=TENANT host=API_HOST port=API_PORT [ ssl=1 ] [ doit=1 ]

default mode is dry run, real updates only with doit=1 flag

if oppty name ends with -NUM then try to increase NUM and recheck
if not - add -1 and recheck

to backup use backupDir param. if backupDir not present it will be created in /tmp
to restore use restoreDir param